        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, then add it to the middle of a <strong>tea towel</strong> and bring the four corners together to form a ball, then twist the ball to squeeze out as much liquid as you can</p><p>Chop the <strong>dried cranberries </strong>and zest 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Add the <strong>grated</strong> <strong>courgette</strong>,<strong> chopped cranberries </strong>and<strong> lemon zest</strong> to the bowl with the 'Nduja</p>",
